text: Sarah Whitmore (born 9 August 1931) is a British equestrian. She competed in the individual dressage event at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:British female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Great Britain Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
